{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 246592,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「い、いかん！？　こんなに離れていても",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"N-No way!? Even from this far away—"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246593,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ワーグ様の力が届いているのか！？\"",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Is Lord Warg's power still reaching us!?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246594,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「おい、お前ら！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hey, you guys!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246595,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　――う、あ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "—Ugh, ah...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246596,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔物兵達は地面に突っ伏すか寝転がり、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The monster soldiers either collapsed onto the ground or lay down,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246597,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "なんと既に半分近くが眠っていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and surprisingly, nearly half of them were already asleep."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246598,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ば、馬鹿者！　目を覚ませ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I-You fools! Wake up!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246599,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ああ！　いや、クソ、無駄か！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ah! No, damn it, is it useless?!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246600,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「全員！　もっとワーグ様から離れろ！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Everyone! Get further away from Lord Warg!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246601,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　急げ！　まだ起きてる奴は連れてけ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hurry! Take those still awake with you!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246602,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「は、はいーーーーッ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-Yesーーー!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246603,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "騒ぎ立てる魔物兵達を",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Amid the noisy monster soldiers,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246604,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ワーグはどこまでも冷たい瞳で眺めていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Warg watched them with endlessly cold eyes."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246605,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「あーらら、大変だ……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Oh dear, this is serious..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246606,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　だから離れてろって伝えたのに」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I told you to keep your distance, you know.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246607,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246608,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふん、くだらない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph, how trivial.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246609,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "リーザスの野営地にランス達が到着した。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and his party arrived at the Lisas camp."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246610,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「よし、戦況を報告しろ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright, report the battle situation.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246611,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はっ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yes, sir.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246612,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「現在のリーザスは集団睡眠事件で、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Currently, Lisas is suffering from a mass sleeping incident,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246613,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　最前線の砦をいくつも落とされている状況です」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and multiple frontline forts have been lost.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246614,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「集団睡眠……ですか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Mass sleeping...is it?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246615,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「なんの前触れもなく、ある日一夜明けると",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Without any warning, one morning after the night passes,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246616,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　兵達が何をしても目覚めなくなるとか……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the soldiers don't wake up no matter what is done to them...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246617,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「殴ろうが、騒ごうが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Whether you hit them or make noise,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246618,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　本当に何をしても目覚めないそうです」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "they truly do not wake up.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246619,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……怖い、ですね……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is... frightening, isn't it...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246620,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そして、それを知っていたように……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And as if they knew this... "
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246621,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　すぐに魔軍が現れ砦は……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "the demon army immediately appeared and the forts were...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246622,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「無抵抗で占領されるってわけだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Occupied without resistance.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246623,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"........\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246624,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "兵は硬い表情のまま、重く頷いた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The soldier nodded heavily with a stern expression."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246625,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「砦だけでなく、街もいくつか落とされました。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Not only forts, some towns have also fallen."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246626,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　眠りから覚めない市民は皆、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The citizens who remain asleep are all"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246627,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　病院に搬送しております」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "being transported to hospitals.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246628,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「砦も街も無抵抗のまま、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Both forts and towns are occupied without resistance,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246629,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔軍に占領されることが相次ぎ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and the demon army is taking them one after another,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246630,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　戦線はガタガタに崩されております……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "causing the frontlines to completely collapse...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246631,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「今までは敵がどれだけ強くとも、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Until now, no matter how strong the enemy was,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246632,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　持ちこたえることは出来たのですが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "we could hold the line, but"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246633,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今回はそれすら……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "this time, even that...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246634,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふん、役立たず共が」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmph, useless lot.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246635,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「どうか、お願いいたします。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Please, we beg of you."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246636,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ランス総統、我らをお救い下さい」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "President Rance, save us.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246637,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ふーむ……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246638,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「とりあえず前線の砦に行ってみるか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"For now, let's go check the frontline forts.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 246639,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ヘルマンの野営地にランス達が到着した。",
